docs.lead_paragraph: FIRST ANNUAL MEETING.--The first annual meeting of the Association for the relief of respectable aged indigent females, will take place this day, at 11 o'clock, A. M., in the Chapel in the Female Academy, Joralemon-street.
docs.snippet: FIRST ANNUAL MEETING.--The first annual meeting of the Association for the relief of respectable aged indigent females, will take place this day, at 11 o'clock, A. M., in the Chapel in the Female Academy, Joralemon-street.

docs.lead_paragraph: MERCANTILE LIBRARY ASSOCIATION.--The annual reports of the Board of Directors and of the Treasurer of this Institution were made at a meeting of the members, which was held on Tuesday evening.
